## Troubleshooting

### App Won't Open
- Force quit and reopen the app
- Restart your device
- Check for iOS updates
- Reinstall the app (your data is stored locally and will remain)

### Data Not Saving
- Ensure you're tapping the "Save" button
- Check that your device has available storage
- Verify iOS permissions haven't been restricted

### History Not Displaying
- Pull down to refresh the history view
- Check if you've recorded any resets yet
- Try force-quitting and reopening the app

### Animations Causing Discomfort
1. Open the **About & Settings** tab
2. Enable **Reduce Motion/Animations**
3. This will disable most app animations

### App Crashes or Freezes
- Force quit the app
- Restart your device
- Ensure you're running the latest iOS version
- Update the app to the latest version
- Contact support if issue persists

