## Privacy & Data

### Your Data is 100% Private

**What stays on your device:**
- All mood entries and reset records
- All notes and observations
- All settings and preferences
- Complete history

**What we DON'T collect:**
- No personal information
- No analytics or usage data
- No location data
- No identifiers
- No device information
- Nothing is sent to external servers

### Data Storage

- All data is stored locally on your iPhone/iPad using encrypted storage
- Data persists across app updates
- Data is included in iCloud/iTunes backups (if enabled on your device)
- Data is NOT synced between devices

### Deleting Your Data

To permanently erase all data:

1. Open the **About & Settings** tab
2. Scroll to **Data & Privacy**
3. Tap **Erase All My Data**
4. Confirm the action

âš ï¸ **Warning**: This action cannot be undone. All reset history, notes, and data will be permanently deleted.

### Uninstalling the App

Deleting the app from your device will also delete all locally stored data. There is no way to recover this data once the app is deleted.

