  - Available 24/7, free and confidential
  - Website: 988lifeline.org

#### International
- **Find a Helpline**
  - Website: [findahelpline.com](https://findahelpline.com)
  - Directory of crisis helplines worldwide
  - Searchable by country

### Accessing Resources in the App

1. Open the **About & Settings** tab
2. Scroll to **Resources**
3. Tap links to call or visit helpline websites

