## FAQ

### Is this app a replacement for therapy?

**No.** If Then Reset is a wellness tool designed to help you manage difficult moments. It is not a replacement for professional mental health care, therapy, diagnosis, or treatment. If you're struggling with mental health, please consult a licensed mental health professional.

### Does the app cost money?

If Then Reset requires a one-time purchase. There are no subscriptions, in-app purchases, or recurring fees.

### Can I sync data between devices?

No. All data stays on your device only. There is no cloud sync or multi-device support. This is by design to protect your privacy.

### How often should I use the app?

Use the app whenever you notice a negative feeling that you want to reset. There's no limit to how many times you can use it per day. Some users reset once a day, others multiple times per hour during difficult periods.

### Which reset technique is best?

The "best" technique is the one that works for you. Experiment with different methods and track which ones help most. Many users have 2-3 favorites they rotate between.

### Will using the app cure my anxiety/depression?

The app is a tool to help manage difficult moments, not a cure. Mental health conditions often require professional treatment, which may include therapy, medication, lifestyle changes, and other interventions. Think of this app as one tool in your wellness toolkit.

### Can I export my data?

Currently, data export is not available. All data remains on your device. We may add export functionality in future updates.

### Why can't I add my own custom feelings or techniques?

Version 1.0 focuses on the 8 most common feelings and 8 evidence-based grounding techniques. We may add customization in future updates based on user feedback.

### Does the app work offline?

Yes! If Then Reset works completely offline. No internet connection is required at any time.

### Is my data backed up?

Your data is included in your device's standard iCloud or iTunes backups (if you have backup enabled in your device settings). However, the app itself does not perform backups to external servers.

### What iOS version do I need?

If Then Reset requires iOS [INSERT MINIMUM VERSION HERE]. Check the App Store listing for specific requirements.

### Can I use this app for kids?

The app is rated 12+ due to mental health content. Parents should supervise children's use and ensure they understand this is a tool, not a replacement for proper care. For children experiencing mental health challenges, consult a pediatric mental health professional.

